<br>
Got attacked by Bandl, waited till he wandered way off, got up, got halfway across the zone and he started hitting me again, along with Iceburg and Tundra Jack.  FD again, watch them all run off, get up and Iceburg comes back and starts attacking me again.  FD again, watch Iceburg walk off to what should be out of agro range, get up and he starts running back.  This went on for 5min when I finally had to quit out.<br>
<br>
Anyone else having this problem with FD?  SK friend of mine in Guk was having it today too. <p>Kragstomper Steinblade<BR>
